<%- include("partials/header"); -%>
<style>
  .container {
    background-color: #f7f7f7;
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }
  .container {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 40px;
    background-color: #fff;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0px 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: 36px;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  p {
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  a {
    color: #337ab7;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>

<div class="homePageBox"></div>
<h1>Welcome to Our Blog!</h1>
<p>Dear readers,</p>
<p>
  We are thrilled to welcome you to our brand new blog! Our aim is to provide
  you with engaging and informative content on a wide range of topics, from
  lifestyle and travel to technology and business.
</p>
<p>
  At our blog, we believe in the power of storytelling. Each post you read is
  written by a member of our team or a guest contributor who has a unique
  perspective to share. We want to inspire and educate you through our words and
  images, and we hope you find our blog to be a valuable resource.
</p>
<p>
  To make sure you don't miss out on any of our latest posts, be sure to
  <a href="/contact">subscribe to our email newsletter</a> and follow us on
  social media. We'll also be hosting giveaways and other fun events, so stay
  tuned!
</p>
<p>
  Thank you for taking the time to visit our blog. We can't wait to start this
  journey with you and see where it takes us.
</p>


<% posts.forEach(function(post) { %>
  <hr>
<h1><%= post.title %></h1>
<p>
  <%= post.content.substring(0, 100) + " ..." %>
  <a href="/posts/<%= post.title %>">Read More</a>
</p>

<% });%> 
</div>
<%- include("partials/footer"); -%>
